{"type": "article", "id": 27233, "title": "“卷起”的刀", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-24T06:49:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 80, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145432usowBAPGgqzRm98S.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>不同于市面上千篇一律的刀，德国设计师 Johanna Gauder 制作的这款 <a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/johannagauder/KNIFE\">One Piece Knife</a> 或许更适合用“艺术品”来形容：它由整块不锈钢制成，看起来就好像是一张微微翘起的白纸，一端经过弯曲形成刀柄，既简洁又美观。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145431aVL0bqHBzDxWXpn8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.433\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145431kHx06eaWjqMbcXyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}